description:
PESTO WITH A PINOY TWIST. When you live in the Philippines and use what you have available ðŸ˜„Hereâ€™s a simple pasta recipe great for beginner and advanced cooks alike. But you do need a blender or food processor. Precise measurements below:

3/4 cup peanuts 
3/4 cup walnuts 
2 garlic cloves 
4 cups basil
2 cups malunggay leaves (or you can use Alugbati, spinach, kale, etc.)
1 1/2 cup olive oil 
1/2 cup coconut oil (or whatever cooking oil you have)
1/2 cup pasta water
1 tablespoon sea salt
Juice from 2-3 kalamansi (or 1 tablespoon lemon juice, or more to taste)
Kalamansi or lemon zest (optional)
Dash of Red pepper flakes 
1/2 kilo (1 pound) pasta noodles
